We're opening a new store almost
every other week or even once a week.

00:24:57.820 --> 00:25:00.200
We're in four different countries,
soon to expand.

00:25:00.360 --> 00:25:03.290
Sales are increasing like crazy.

00:25:03.300 --> 00:25:05.960
In the mall locations,
our sales per square foot are

00:25:05.960 --> 00:25:07.670
higher than anybody around us.

00:25:07.780 --> 00:25:12.670
So, what are we looking for in order
to come into the retail assortment?

00:25:12.680 --> 00:25:16.840
And I gotta say, on a daily basis,
we're constantly looking for new,

00:25:16.870 --> 00:25:20.080
great applications out there,
and would love to look at

00:25:20.320 --> 00:25:23.290
everything that's out there,
add to our assortment.

00:25:23.300 --> 00:25:25.830
We're constantly changing,
and when applicable,

00:25:25.830 --> 00:25:29.610
if we've got a lot of great new apps,
we can always figure out a way

00:25:29.710 --> 00:25:33.340
to get more space allocated
and add some things in.

00:25:33.340 --> 00:25:35.470
So, I think this bodes well
for everybody here.

00:25:35.570 --> 00:25:38.720
So, if we were to have a meeting
and talk about getting a

00:25:38.800 --> 00:25:41.960
product into Apple retail,
what kinds of things would the

00:25:41.960 --> 00:25:43.740
Apple retail buyer be looking for?

00:25:43.740 --> 00:25:44.830
So, let's start with product.

00:25:44.920 --> 00:25:47.780
So, I have this up here,
consumer-focused.

00:25:47.780 --> 00:25:51.240
If you look at the retail stores and
