We're seeing 2 million people per week.

00:25:59.310 --> 00:26:01.160
Incredible amount of
traffic coming through.

00:26:01.160 --> 00:26:04.210
Lots of demographics,
but the vast majority of the people

00:26:04.210 --> 00:26:06.050
that we're seeing are consumers.

00:26:06.220 --> 00:26:10.470
And I say consumer as opposed
to the business customer,

00:26:10.830 --> 00:26:13.390
but keep in mind,
for those of you that have a productivity

00:26:13.390 --> 00:26:17.270
application or a high-end graphics app,
we still do a high amount of

00:26:17.270 --> 00:26:19.430
sales to business customers.

