00:34:48.960 --> 00:34:49.780
I talked to Robert.

00:34:49.780 --> 00:34:51.930
I said, well, you're coming to the
developers conference,

00:34:51.930 --> 00:34:52.500
aren't you?

00:34:52.500 --> 00:34:53.480
Well, I'm not sure.

00:34:53.480 --> 00:34:57.600
And I talk him into coming and hook
