00:35:11.580 --> 00:35:15.180
So great filters in the application,
so forth.

00:35:15.280 --> 00:35:16.720
Great developer story.

00:35:16.720 --> 00:35:19.840
He also tells me, you know,
those eyesight cameras,

00:35:19.840 --> 00:35:23.300
you can plug them in, take your picture,
plug it into the comic

00:35:23.850 --> 00:35:25.580
strip that you're building.

00:35:28.720 --> 00:35:30.690
Well,
