00:35:43.090 --> 00:35:44.670
actually integrated with .Mac.

00:35:44.890 --> 00:35:50.310
You make this beautiful comic,
hit a button, it's published to the .Mac

00:35:50.310 --> 00:35:52.250
-- to your .Mac web page.

00:35:52.580 --> 00:35:54.460
And that's something I really
encourage you to think about.

00:35:54.530 --> 00:36:01.510
There's so many creative things
you can do and easily -- by easily

00:36:01.510 --> 00:36:01.510
integrating with the .Mac service.

00:36:01.960 --> 00:36:04.940
After that, they get connected with a
