00:36:22.960 --> 00:36:27.620
We want it on the machines." So now,
every Mac that goes out the

00:36:27.620 --> 00:36:30.000
door is bundled with Comic Life.

00:36:30.040 --> 00:36:34.850
It's a great story about how a small
developer really took advantage

00:36:34.900 --> 00:36:38.510
of all the things that we offer,
put it together,

00:36:38.510 --> 00:36:40.670
